1
00:01:10,666 --> 00:01:12,750
It's time to begin
our first game.

2
00:01:12,833 --> 00:01:16,708
We have Class 1 versus
Class 7. Take your positions!

3
00:01:17,916 --> 00:01:20,750
[YAMANE] Today is Sports Day
and we're playing soccer.

4
00:01:20,833 --> 00:01:22,833
[yelping]

5
00:01:22,916 --> 00:01:24,083
I don't know what I'm doing!

6
00:01:24,166 --> 00:01:27,375
Somebody take it!
Somebody take it, please!

7
00:01:32,833 --> 00:01:34,958
[KURIHARA]
Yamane!

8
00:01:35,041 --> 00:01:36,583
Go! Beat Class 1!

9
00:01:36,666 --> 00:01:37,916
[YAMANE]
Kurihara!

10
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:40,833
[YAMANE]
I just wanna go back to bed!

11
00:01:42,125 --> 00:01:43,791
[yells]

12
00:01:43,875 --> 00:01:46,333
[KANDA]
Go Takase!

13
00:01:46,416 --> 00:01:49,083
[KANDA] But if I cheer for him,
is it obvious that I like him?

14
00:01:49,166 --> 00:01:52,000
[KANDA, MINAGAWA]
Yeah! Goal! All right Class 1!

15
00:01:52,083 --> 00:01:54,291
[TAKASE] Can I look at Kanda
while she's cheering?

16
00:01:54,375 --> 00:01:56,666
Or would that be too obvious?

17
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:09,083
[NORO]
Furuya! Pass it!

18
00:02:10,125 --> 00:02:13,916
[HOTARU] Go, Big Brother!
Come on, Furuya! Score!

19
00:02:15,458 --> 00:02:17,041
[NORO]
Yo, Goda!

20
00:02:17,125 --> 00:02:19,750
Looks like it's down to
just your class and mine.

21
00:02:19,833 --> 00:02:20,375
Yeah.

22
00:02:20,458 --> 00:02:21,541
You're goin' down.

23
00:02:21,625 --> 00:02:23,166
We don't have girlfriends
distracting us.

24
00:02:23,250 --> 00:02:24,833
We won't if you keep
handling the ball.

25
00:02:24,916 --> 00:02:27,750
You know you can't, right?

26
00:02:27,833 --> 00:02:30,333
What? Why can't I?

27
00:02:30,416 --> 00:02:31,500
I do in volleyball.

28
00:02:31,583 --> 00:02:32,166
[GODA]
This is soccer.

29
00:02:32,250 --> 00:02:33,791
[NORO]
No fair!

30
00:02:33,875 --> 00:02:36,625
Hey! Good luck in the finals.
I'll be rooting for you.

31
00:02:36,708 --> 00:02:38,666
Thanks, Hosokawa!

32
00:02:38,750 --> 00:02:40,541
Don't you have something
to say to him, too?

33
00:02:40,625 --> 00:02:42,833
Um. Well...

34
00:02:42,916 --> 00:02:44,291
Fine. Don't say anything.

35
00:02:44,375 --> 00:02:46,458
You're a real jackass!

36
00:02:46,541 --> 00:02:47,583
[PATRICIA]
Keisuke.

37
00:02:47,666 --> 00:02:48,791
[KEISUKE]
Uh?

38
00:02:48,875 --> 00:02:50,541
I wanna play in the
boys' soccer final, too.

39
00:02:50,625 --> 00:02:51,750
I'm not sure that's allowed.

40
00:02:51,833 --> 00:02:52,791
[TEACHER A]
She can play.

41
00:02:52,875 --> 00:02:54,166
I'll just have
someone switch out.

42
00:02:54,250 --> 00:02:56,125
[KEISUKE] Seriously? But
who's she gonna switch with?

43
00:02:56,208 --> 00:02:57,750
Can I have your spot?

44
00:02:57,833 --> 00:02:59,541
[KEISUKE]
Mh-hm...

45
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:01,916
All right. Final game.
Winner takes all.

46
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,125
[ALL]
Go Class 1! You can do it!

47
00:03:04,208 --> 00:03:06,083
Yo! You can leave Goda to me.

48
00:03:06,166 --> 00:03:08,041
Sure. Just don't use your hands.

49
00:03:08,125 --> 00:03:10,000
[NORO]
I'll remember. Don't worry.

50
00:03:10,083 --> 00:03:11,375
Hey, goalie. You ready?

51
00:03:11,458 --> 00:03:12,583
Yeah.

52
00:03:12,666 --> 00:03:14,208
[PATRICIA]
Hmph.

53
00:03:14,291 --> 00:03:15,333
Bring it!

54
00:03:15,416 --> 00:03:17,166
[CLASS 1 BOYS]
Uh...

55
00:03:17,250 --> 00:03:18,916
[whistle blows]

56
00:03:23,708 --> 00:03:26,083
Sugawara is such an
amazing soccer player.

57
00:03:26,166 --> 00:03:27,166
Yeah, he is.

58
00:03:27,250 --> 00:03:28,000
See that kick?

59
00:03:28,083 --> 00:03:28,958
Very powerful.

60
00:03:29,041 --> 00:03:30,208
Look at him go!

61
00:03:30,291 --> 00:03:33,833
Why do you keep telling
me to watch Sugawara?

62
00:03:33,916 --> 00:03:37,125
[SUGAWARA] Is Takano here?
Is she watching me play?

63
00:03:37,208 --> 00:03:40,583
Why can't I let it go? I know
I don't stand a chance.

64
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:47,541
[gasps]

65
00:03:47,625 --> 00:03:48,625
[SUGAWARA gasps]

66
00:03:56,541 --> 00:03:59,416
[CHIAKI]
Oh. Ugh, that hurt.

67
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:04,041
[KANA]
Hey. Thanks, Chiaki.

68
00:04:04,125 --> 00:04:06,250
[CHIAKI]
Yeah. Don't read much into it.

69
00:04:06,333 --> 00:04:07,750
I was only trying
to get the ball.

70
00:04:07,833 --> 00:04:10,541
[KANA] What? The ball was
already ours! You didn't have...

71
00:04:10,625 --> 00:04:11,958
[CHIAKI]
So? I saved you! And a minute...

72
00:04:12,041 --> 00:04:13,041
[KANA]
Saved me?

73
00:04:13,125 --> 00:04:14,333
I don't need your
help, you moron!

74
00:04:14,416 --> 00:04:15,583
What's wrong?
Trouble in paradise?

75
00:04:15,666 --> 00:04:17,291
[CHIAKI, KANA] Shut up!
Mind your own business!

76
00:04:17,375 --> 00:04:19,125
You poor saps with girlfriends.

77
00:04:19,208 --> 00:04:20,875
You're whipped,
every last one of ya.

78
00:04:20,958 --> 00:04:23,666
[CHIAKI] Hey, Noro, the
ball wasn't out of play.

79
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,625
Dammit! You tricked me!

80
00:04:34,125 --> 00:04:35,708
[CLASS 1 GIRLS cheering]

81
00:04:35,791 --> 00:04:37,625
[ALL]
Aww...

82
00:04:37,708 --> 00:04:39,791
[MATSUURA] We don't want
Class 4 to lose, do we?

83
00:04:39,875 --> 00:04:41,125
Let's get the boys fired up!

84
00:04:41,208 --> 00:04:42,583
[CLASS 4 GIRLS]
Yeah!

85
00:04:42,666 --> 00:04:44,750
[MATSUURA]
Ready. Go Class 4!

86
00:04:44,833 --> 00:04:49,458
[CLASS 4 GIRLS] Go Class 4!
Go Class 4! Go Class 4!

87
00:04:49,541 --> 00:04:51,500
[CHIAKI]
Kana's not part of that, is she?

88
00:04:51,583 --> 00:04:53,625
There's no way
she'd cheer for me.

89
00:04:53,708 --> 00:04:55,250
Then again, what did I expect?

90
00:04:55,333 --> 00:04:57,833
We're broken up.
Why would she care?

91
00:04:58,875 --> 00:05:01,000
[KANA]
Chiaki!

92
00:05:01,083 --> 00:05:02,166
Quit screwin' around!

93
00:05:02,250 --> 00:05:04,583
You can run faster
than that! Hurry it up!

94
00:05:04,666 --> 00:05:06,583
[CHIAKI]
Jeez. What's her problem?

95
00:05:06,666 --> 00:05:08,708
Is that supposed to
be cheering me on?

96
00:05:08,791 --> 00:05:12,666
Hey. I'm talkin' to
you, you moron!

97
00:05:17,333 --> 00:05:18,583
Chiaki!

98
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:26,750
[CHIAKI] Dammit, Kana,
you broke up with me.

99
00:05:26,833 --> 00:05:28,958
You're not my
girlfriend anymore.

100
00:05:30,666 --> 00:05:32,625
[CHIAKI] You really think
screaming that I'm a moron

101
00:05:32,708 --> 00:05:34,208
at the top of your lungs
is going make me

102
00:05:34,291 --> 00:05:36,083
want to get back together?

103
00:05:36,166 --> 00:05:37,916
Well, it shouldn't, but it does!

104
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,583
It makes me wanna be
your boyfriend again!

105
00:05:40,666 --> 00:05:43,250
Run! Chiaki!

106
00:05:43,333 --> 00:05:45,250
[CHIAKI]
For you, Kana!

107
00:05:48,541 --> 00:05:49,875
And save!

108
00:05:49,958 --> 00:05:51,750
[CHIAKI]
No!

109
00:05:51,833 --> 00:05:53,208
Ha! Nice try!

110
00:05:53,291 --> 00:05:55,791
But a sucker like you isn't
gonna take me down! Ha-ha!

111
00:05:55,875 --> 00:05:57,333
I wouldn't bet on it, Noro!

112
00:05:57,416 --> 00:06:00,125
I work out every day!
You don't have a prayer!

113
00:06:04,541 --> 00:06:07,583
Oh, yeah!

114
00:06:07,666 --> 00:06:10,958
[ALL]
Go Pattie!

115
00:06:11,041 --> 00:06:14,083
[PATRICIA]
High five! High five! Woo!

116
00:06:14,166 --> 00:06:15,708
[ALL grumble]

117
00:06:18,625 --> 00:06:20,000
[TEACHER A]
And last but not least,

118
00:06:20,083 --> 00:06:22,875
be sure to keep your nose clean
and stay out of trouble.

119
00:06:22,958 --> 00:06:24,708
[STUDENTS]
Yes, ma'am.

120
00:06:24,791 --> 00:06:26,208
So hey,

121
00:06:26,291 --> 00:06:28,125
is the soccer team gonna have
practice over the summer?

122
00:06:28,208 --> 00:06:30,875
Uh, yeah. Pretty sure.

123
00:06:30,958 --> 00:06:33,041
A bunch of us are all
planning to go to the beach.

124
00:06:33,125 --> 00:06:34,583
It'd be great if you could come.

125
00:06:34,666 --> 00:06:35,750
[SUGAWARA]
Hmm...

126
00:06:35,833 --> 00:06:37,375
Depends on what coach says.

127
00:06:37,458 --> 00:06:39,833
Takano is supposed to be there.

128
00:06:39,916 --> 00:06:41,500
[gasps]

129
00:06:41,583 --> 00:06:44,375
[TAKANO] The beach?
No thanks. That's not for me.

130
00:06:44,458 --> 00:06:46,625
I'm shy about wearing
a bathing suit.

131
00:06:46,708 --> 00:06:48,208
[YOSHINAGA]
I know. So am I.

132
00:06:48,291 --> 00:06:51,833
But everybody's going.
Kamine, Goda, Pattie.

133
00:06:51,916 --> 00:06:53,666
I'd really hate for
you to miss it.

134
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,875
I don't know. I'm not
really sure I'd like it.

135
00:06:55,958 --> 00:06:58,875
Sugawara's going to come.

136
00:06:58,958 --> 00:07:00,000
See ya!

137
00:07:00,083 --> 00:07:01,583
[PATRICIA]
Bye!

138
00:07:03,333 --> 00:07:06,666
Look, Kana. Chiaki's all
alone. Go make up with him.

139
00:07:08,250 --> 00:07:09,458
Okay. Hey.

140
00:07:09,541 --> 00:07:10,791
[SUGAWARA]
Hey, Chiaki?

141
00:07:10,875 --> 00:07:12,625
You're going to the beach
with everybody, right?

142
00:07:12,708 --> 00:07:15,500
[CHIAKI] Not sure yet.
But I was thinking about it.

143
00:07:15,583 --> 00:07:18,416
If, uh, I came too,
would that be okay?

144
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:19,500
[CHIAKI]
Why not?

145
00:07:19,583 --> 00:07:21,583
Matsuura told me that
Takano's going.

146
00:07:21,666 --> 00:07:22,875
And I'm worried
that with me there,

147
00:07:22,958 --> 00:07:24,958
things could get
a little awkward.

148
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:30,458
I live for awkward.
Please come.

149
00:07:30,541 --> 00:07:32,333
Wait, so Sugawara's not coming?

150
00:07:32,416 --> 00:07:33,625
[MATSUURA]
He said he didn't know,

151
00:07:33,708 --> 00:07:36,208
that he'd have to ask
his soccer coach first.

152
00:07:36,291 --> 00:07:37,625
Oh.

153
00:07:37,708 --> 00:07:40,458
What about you? You and Takano
are in for sure, right?

154
00:07:40,541 --> 00:07:42,125
Yeah!

155
00:07:46,958 --> 00:07:48,541
[KANA]
You have do this, Kana.

156
00:07:48,625 --> 00:07:50,958
If you try to meet Chiaki
once summer break starts,

157
00:07:51,041 --> 00:07:52,583
it'll just be weird.

158
00:07:52,666 --> 00:07:54,333
All right, I sent it.

159
00:07:54,416 --> 00:07:56,250
Now will he stay?

160
00:08:00,291 --> 00:08:02,416
[CHIAKI]
Crap. My battery's dead.

161
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:04,208
[TAKASE] ♪ I don't know,
but I've been told. ♪

162
00:08:04,291 --> 00:08:05,458
[PLAYERS]
♪ I don't know... ♪

163
00:08:05,541 --> 00:08:07,416
[SUGAWARA] I could go to
the beach if I wanted.

164
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:09,458
There's actually no
practice that day.

165
00:08:09,541 --> 00:08:10,833
But if I do,

166
00:08:10,916 --> 00:08:12,958
it'll get me thinking about
Takano all over again.

167
00:08:13,041 --> 00:08:15,333
Even if I know she's
not interested.

168
00:08:15,416 --> 00:08:16,833
Just come to the beach.

169
00:08:16,916 --> 00:08:19,166
She doesn't know or care,
so why should you?

170
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:20,541
[SUGAWARA]
But that's just it.

171
00:08:20,625 --> 00:08:23,375
Going when she doesn't care
would make me miserable.

172
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,916
[KANA]
It's not even marked as "read."

173
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:32,958
Oh, Chiaki. Did you
really go home?

174
00:08:33,041 --> 00:08:35,708
Hey. Is it all right
if we practice?

175
00:08:37,125 --> 00:08:38,833
What's the big rush, Sugawara?

176
00:08:38,916 --> 00:08:40,083
I forgot something.

177
00:08:40,166 --> 00:08:43,208
So are you gonna come
to the beach, or what?

178
00:08:43,291 --> 00:08:44,583
Don't think so.

179
00:08:44,666 --> 00:08:46,291
[YOSHINAGA] If Sugawara
doesn't come to the beach,

180
00:08:46,375 --> 00:08:49,125
it'll suck, won't it?

181
00:08:49,208 --> 00:08:50,541
[TAKANO]
What?

182
00:08:50,625 --> 00:08:53,916
Will you be upset if he doesn't?
Do you still like him?

183
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:57,625
[YOSHINAGA]
Uh, no. Not anymore.

184
00:08:57,708 --> 00:08:59,333
But I knew he didn't
have feelings for me,

185
00:08:59,416 --> 00:09:01,875
so I never had a
chance to begin with.

186
00:09:01,958 --> 00:09:04,916
Oh. I didn't realize that.

187
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,916
[YOSHINAGA]
What about you? Do you like him?

188
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,291
Me?

189
00:09:11,875 --> 00:09:13,375
[KANA]
Guess Chiaki lost interest

190
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:15,583
in trying to patch things up.

191
00:09:17,541 --> 00:09:19,333
[KANA]
Looks like he really left.

192
00:09:19,416 --> 00:09:22,375
And I'll be spending this
summer by myself.

193
00:09:26,416 --> 00:09:28,291
[YOSHINAGA]
Sorry. I shouldn't have asked.

194
00:09:28,375 --> 00:09:31,166
Be right back. I'm gonna
run to the bathroom.

195
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:32,625
[TAKANO]
Okay.

196
00:09:35,333 --> 00:09:37,208
[TAKANO]
Do I like Sugawara?

197
00:09:37,291 --> 00:09:40,208
I am always thinking
about him lately.

198
00:09:43,083 --> 00:09:44,833
[TAKANO] And if he doesn't
come to the beach,

199
00:09:44,916 --> 00:09:47,166
I think I would be upset.

200
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:50,958
[footsteps]

201
00:09:51,041 --> 00:09:53,583
Yoshinaga? Everything okay?

202
00:09:58,541 --> 00:10:01,458
Took you long enough.
Were you doing something?

203
00:10:01,541 --> 00:10:04,125
[KANA] I sent you a text.
Didn't you see it?

204
00:10:04,208 --> 00:10:05,208
[CHIAKI gasps]

205
00:10:05,291 --> 00:10:06,916
Sorry. Dead battery.

206
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,458
And I was waiting for you
so we could talk in person.

207
00:10:09,541 --> 00:10:10,625
Why did you wanna talk?

208
00:10:10,708 --> 00:10:13,125
Were you going to try
and fix things?

209
00:10:15,041 --> 00:10:18,875
No. We've broken up.
What's done is done.

210
00:10:18,958 --> 00:10:21,375
What are you doing here?
Is something wrong?

211
00:10:21,458 --> 00:10:23,416
No. I left my wallet.

212
00:10:24,583 --> 00:10:27,458
[SUGAWARA] What about you?
Practicing all alone?

213
00:10:27,541 --> 00:10:30,500
Not alone. Yoshinaga's
in the bathroom.

214
00:10:30,583 --> 00:10:31,958
Oh, I see.

215
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:35,916
[SUGAWARA]
Bye then!

216
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,625
Are you going to come
to the beach, Sugawara?

217
00:10:38,708 --> 00:10:40,333
But if I'm being honest,

218
00:10:40,416 --> 00:10:43,333
I didn't think you'd ever break
up with me no matter what I did.

219
00:10:43,416 --> 00:10:45,875
I took you for granted.

220
00:10:45,958 --> 00:10:47,708
If we were to pretend
that never happened

221
00:10:47,791 --> 00:10:49,416
and try to go back to
the way things were,

222
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:51,416
it wouldn't be right.

223
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:55,166
I'd feel bad. Relationships
like that don't last.

224
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:56,916
So let's end it.

225
00:10:58,625 --> 00:11:00,541
And once everything's
over and done with,

226
00:11:00,625 --> 00:11:02,500
I wanna start again.

227
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,208
[SUGAWARA]
Oh, yeah, the beach trip.

228
00:11:08,291 --> 00:11:10,250
Well, I kinda decided
I'm not going to go.

229
00:11:10,333 --> 00:11:11,916
Why not? Soccer practice?

230
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,166
[SUGAWARA]
Nah.

231
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:16,375
The beach just really
isn't my thing, ya know?

232
00:11:16,458 --> 00:11:17,791
But I heard you
were going, right?

233
00:11:17,875 --> 00:11:19,583
I hope you have lots of fun.

234
00:11:19,666 --> 00:11:22,916
I don't think I'll have any
fun if you're not there.

235
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:30,500
[KANA] Fine. Tell me
you have feelings for me.

236
00:11:30,583 --> 00:11:32,291
I'll reject you a hundred times.

237
00:11:32,375 --> 00:11:34,458
[CHIAKI]
Then I'll say it a 101.

238
00:11:34,541 --> 00:11:36,541
You better mean it, understand?

239
00:11:36,625 --> 00:11:38,291
[CHIAKI]
Okay.

240
00:11:38,375 --> 00:11:41,500
I love you. You're more
than my best friend.

241
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:46,416
So please, will you
go out with me?

242
00:11:54,791 --> 00:11:56,166
[KANA]
Okay.

243
00:11:57,791 --> 00:12:00,250
If that's the case...

244
